T1  - Uniqueness of Cournot Equilibrium: New Results From Old Methods
PY  - 1991
Y1  - 1991/04/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297975
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 58
IS  - 2
SP  - 399
EP  - 404
SN  - 0034-6527
AB  - This paper provides sufficient conditions for the existence of a unique Cournot equilibrium. Previous uniqueness results have depended on an assumption of non-degeneracy of equilibrium. As we illustrate, this assumption often fails in multi-stage games with proper Cournot subgames. Since our uniqueness results do not depend on this assumption, they are more widely applicable.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/2297975
ER  - 



